nodes.text: Wonga winga cingee wooze, which of these do I choose

Wonga winga cingee wooze, which of these do I choose was a choosing game that was taught in the First Order's Stormtrooper Corps. Former stormtrooper Finn and Resistance technician Rose Tico played the game when trying to determine which way they would go in a sewer on Canto Bight on Cantonica.
"Wonga winga cingee wooze" first canonically appeared in the novelization Star Wars: The Last Jedi: Expanded Edition.
